SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT A.* FROM TZUMEN_LIST A INNER JOIN ( SELECT Customer_Code, max(seq_no) AS SEQ_NO FROM TZUMEN_LIST WHERE ZUMEN_TITLE_ID='343' AND customer_code =':1' GROUP BY Customer_Code ) B ON A.Customer_Code = B.Customer_Code AND A.Seq_no = B.Seq_no WHERE ZUMEN_TITLE_ID='343'

SELECT B.*
FROM ( SELECT A.CUSTOMER_CODE, Max(A.SEQ_NO) AS SEQ_NO
FROM ( SELECT * FROM TZUMEN_LIST WHERE ZUMEN_TITLE_ID='343' ) A
WHERE A.DELETE_FLG = 0 GROUP BY A.CUSTOMER_CODE )A
INNER JOIN ( SELECT * FROM TZUMEN_LIST WHERE ZUMEN_TITLE_ID='343' )B
ON A.SEQ_NO = B.SEQ_NO AND A.CUSTOMER_CODE = B.CUSTOMER_CODE
WHERE to_char(B.UPDATE_DAY,'YYYY/MM/DD') >= '2016/01/01'

SELECT A.*,B.DBCadVersion
FROM W_ModuleMonitoringSheet_W_NaisIchijoData A
LEFT JOIN (SELECT B.ConstructionCode, '' AS 'DBCadVersion' FROM W_ModuleMonitoringSheet_W_NaisIchijoData A INNER JOIN HRDSQL4.PHOTOVOLTAIC.DBO.SPCadCLInfos_Cad B ON A.CustomerCode = B.ConstructionCode) B ON A.CustomerCode = B.ConstructionCode
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ConstructionCode FROM HRDSQL4.PHOTOVOLTAIC.DBO.SpcadPlanInfos B) C ON A.CustomerCode = C.ConstructionCode
WHERE C.ConstructionCode IS NULL

SELECT A., A., A., A., A., A., A., A., A., A., A.SPCAD, A.kw, A.kw, A.kw, A.kw, A.PanelModelNo1, A.PanelCnt1, A.PanelModelNo2, A.PanelCnt2, A.PanelModelNo3, A.PanelCnt3, A.PanelModelNo4,A.PanelCnt4, A.ModuleKind, A.ModuleDetail, A.ModuleNumber, A.PanelDirection, A.Qty, A.RequestYear, A.RequestWeek, A.RequestDestination, C.FilingUploaded, C.FilingRemarks, A.UpdatedDate AS DB, A., A.,
CASE WHEN [] IS NOT NULL AND [FilingUploaded] IS NULL THEN 'NG' WHEN ( [FilingUploaded] >= '2016/01/01' OR [UpdatedDate] >= '2016/01/01' ) AND DATEDIFF(d, FilingUploaded, UpdatedDate) <> 0 AND DATEDIFF(d, FilingUploaded, UpdatedDate) <> 1 AND DATEDIFF(d, FilingUploaded, updateddate) <> -1 THEN 'Check' ELSE NULL END AS NG
FROM W_ModuleMonitoringSheet_W903 A LEFT JOIN F001_720205_Plans_ModuleMonitoringSheet B ON A. = B.ConstructionCode LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM W_ModuleMonitoringSheet_W907) C
ON A. = C.CUSTOMERCODE ORDER BY A., A., A.ModuleKind
